query:
SELECT t.name as task_name, w.name as workflow_name, c.name as customer_name
                  FROM tasks t
                  INNER JOIN workflows w ON t.workflow_id = w.id
                  INNER JOIN customers c ON w.customer_id = c.id
                  LIMIT 15
